npm install -g @vue/cli - to install vue cli
vue create my-project - to create new project 
vue config - if creating project is very slow , do this and go in there and change it false 
npm run serve - to run the server 

error: trailing spaces not allowed in vue js
solution: I think its a vscode issue. Try the following:
In vscode go to settings ( ctrl+, )
In settings search bar type "trim trailing whitespace"
Underneath check "trim trailing whitespace" option.
Restart vscode


